"Le suivi de la dénutrition (rappels de re-cotation MNA, apports vs besoins, "
"hydratation) s'appuie sur les registres cliniques et le module de soins. "
"Voir [Les registres cliniques](../soins/registres.md)."

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:130
msgid "OHAT — oral health"
msgstr "OHAT — santé bucco-dentaire"

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:132
msgid ""
"The **OHAT** (Oral Health Assessment Tool) assesses **oral health** across "
"**8 categories**, scored from 0 (healthy) to 2 (needs treatment): lips, "
"tongue, gums and tissues, saliva, natural teeth, dentures, oral cleanliness "
"and dental pain."
msgstr ""
"L'**OHAT** (Oral Health Assessment Tool) évalue la **santé bucco-dentaire** "
"en **8 catégories**, cotées de 0 (sain) à 2 (à traiter) : lèvres, langue, "
"gencives et tissus, salive, dents naturelles, prothèses, propreté buccale et"
" douleur dentaire."

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:137
msgid ""
"The total ranges from 0 to 16. **Here, the higher the score, the more "
"concerning the situation.**"
msgstr ""
"Le total va de 0 à 16. **Ici, plus le score est haut, plus la situation est "
"préoccupante.**"

